unk_9c63f9d.value:
OWC_SMP_CHECK()
for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("SMP_Brawl_Crowd")) do
	Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(actorID, AISTATE_TAUNT)
	Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(actorID, 0, true)
end

if bHasLunatic and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLunatic) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idVictim) then
	Hydra.QActorPower(idLunatic, POWER_LUNATIC_SUICIDE, idLunatic)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLunatic)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idVictim) then
		Hydra.ActorKill(idVictim)	
	end

else
	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "initialMonsters")) do
		Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(actorID, AISTATE_BRAWLER)
		Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(actorID, 0, true)
	end
end

unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idActorSpawned, AISTATE_TAUNT, idActorSpawned, 0)
	Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(idActorSpawned, 3, true)
end

unk_993f312.value:
bElite = Events.SMPShouldBeElite(idSelf)
bHasLunatic = false

-- spawn monsters
for i, spawnerID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "spawners")) do
	Events.ActorEnableSpawner(spawnerID)
end

-- chance to spawn elite
if bElite then
	for i, spawnerID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "elite")) do
		Events.ActorEnableSpawner(spawnerID)
	end
end

for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "initialMonsters")) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsArchetype(actorID, "lunatic") then
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(actorID, AISTATE_TAUNT, actorID, 0)
		bHasLunatic = true
		if idLunatic == nil then
			idLunatic = actorID
		else
			idVictim = actorID
		end
	else
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(actorID, AISTATE_BRAWLER, actorID, 0)
		idVictim = actorID
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(actorID, 3, true)
end
